Li not buying Sun Fook Kong stake - paper . Li Ka - shing , chairman of Cheung Kong ( Holdings ) Ltd , has decided not to take a stake in construction and civil engineering firm Sun Fook Kong Holdings Ltd , the Hong Kong Economic Journal said on Saturday . Last week , China Travel International Investment Hong Kong Ltd said it teamed up with Li and Albert Chow to take a stake in Sun Fook Kong . Li was not immediately available to comment on the newspaper report . Chow is a former deputy managing director of Cheung Kong and is currently a non - executive director . - - Hong Kong Newsroom ( 852 ) 2843 6590 
